# Borek Finance branding

Before building or styling any UI, read [BRANDING.md](../../BRANDING.md) and use [branding/theme.css](../../branding/theme.css).

## Hard rules

- Product: **Borek Finance** (repo: Finance-AI). Parent: Borek Solutions Group.
- **No new colours** — only CSS variables from `branding/theme.css` (`--navy-700`, `--accent`, `--fg1`, etc.).
- Page background: `--navy-700` (#0D123F). Accent: `--accent` (#DB3714), used sparingly.
- Import theme in frontend entry: `import '../branding/theme.css'` (adjust path as needed).
- Use existing classes: `.eyebrow`, `.card`, `.btn-accent`, `.btn-ghost`, `.data-table`, `.upload-zone`, `.badge--*`.
- No emoji, no exclamation marks, British spelling, sentence-case headlines.
- Cards: no default shadows. Buttons: pills. Motion: `--ease`, no bounce.
